<CATEGORY> sports </CATEGORY>
<HEADLINE> Needs and Wants of NBA Teams </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	A team-by-team look at the needs and possibilities for each of  
the 29 NBA teams 
</P>
<P>
 *EASTERN CONFERENCE   	
</P>
<P>
 *Atlantic Division    	
</P>
<P>
 *MIAMI HEAT (33-17, eliminated 3-2 by New York in first round).    	
</P>
<P>
	Needs: Perimeter shooting, bench strength.  
</P>
<P>
	Salary cap room: None.  
</P>
<P>
	Top free agents: Dan Majerle, Rex Walters, Terry Porter.  
</P>
<P>
	Rumor mill: If they can lure Charles Oakley, would look to move  
P.J. Brown to the Lakers for Glen Rice. 
</P>
<P>
 *ORLANDO MAGIC (33-17, eliminated 3-1 by Philadelphia in first  
round). 
</P>
<P>
	Needs: Power forward, post-Penny scoring.  
</P>
<P>
	Salary cap room: None.  
</P>
<P>
	Top free agents: Bo Outlaw.  
</P>
<P>
	Rumor mill: Outlaw will stay, Penny Hardaway will be dealt to  
the Lakers, Raptors, Trail Blazers or Suns. 
</P>
<P>
 *PHILADELPHIA 76ers (28-22, eliminated 4-0 by Indiana in second  
round). 
</P>
<P>
	Needs: Low post depth, offensive options.  
</P>
<P>
	Salary cap room: None.  
</P>
<P>
	Top free agents: Eric Snow, George Lynch.  
</P>
<P>
	Rumor mill: Will re-sign Snow and keep him, could send Lynch to  
Clippers in sign-and-trade deal for Rodney Rogers. 
</P>
<P>
 *NEW YORK KNICKS (27-23, lost NBA Finals 4-1 to San Antonio).    	
</P>
<P>
	Needs: Perimeter shooting, low post depth.  
</P>
<P>
	Salary cap room: None.  
</P>
<P>
	Top free agents: None.  
</P>
<P>
	Rumor mill: Interested in free agents Dell Curry and Otis  
Thorpe. 
</P>
<P>
 *BOSTON CELTICS (19-31, missed playoffs)    	
</P>
<P>
	Needs: Semi-major overhaul.  
</P>
<P>
	Salary cap room: None.  
</P>
<P>
	Top free agents: None.  
</P>
<P>
	Rumor mill: Ron Mercer is available via trade to the highest  
bidder, with Dallas looking to get him for Samaki Walker and a No. 
1 pick. Antoine Walker and Kenny Anderson also on trading block. 
</P>
<P>
 *WASHINGTON WIZARDS (18-32, missed playoffs).    	
</P>
<P>
	Needs: A shooter and a center.  
</P>
<P>
	Salary cap room: None.  
</P>
<P>
	Top free agents: Mitch Richmond, Otis Thorpe, Calbert Cheaney.  
</P>
<P>
