<HEADLINE> Mrs. Tom Hanks Happily Anonymous </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEW YORK (AP) -- Rita Wilson may not be as famous as husband Tom  
Hanks, but the actress doesn't have any complaints. 
</P>
<P>
	``People say that it must be really hard on me that Tom is so  
successful,'' Wilson said in the August edition of More magazine. 
</P>
<P>
	``I have a successful family. I work. I have great friends.  
People say, 'If you weren't married to Tom, you'd be successful 
too.' It cracks me up. I mean, I am successful, in what I want,'' 
she said. 
</P>
<P>
	Wilson and Hanks have been married for 10 years, and have  
appeared together in movies such as ``Sleepless in Seattle.'' 
Wilson also stars in the new movie ``Runaway Bride,'' with Richard 
Gere and Julia Roberts. 
  	   	
</P>
</TEXT>
