and tax cuts. Guests: Jimmy Mercer, Henry County, Ga., police 
chief; Rep. Carolyn McCarthy, D-N.Y.; Sens. Jeff Sessions, R-Ala., 
John Breaux, D-La., and Phil Gramm, R-Texas. 

