<HEADLINE> Excerpts From Tripp-Lewinsky Tapes </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	Excerpts from more than 20 hours of tape recordings that Linda  
Tripp made of conversations with Monica Lewinsky, released Oct. 2 
as part of evidence referred to the House Judiciary Committee by 
Independent Counsel Kenneth Starr. The tapes were made between Oct. 
3 and Dec. 22, 1997; the date of each conversation was not apparent 
in the transcripts. 
</P>
